Privacy policy

1. Introduction
This Privacy Policy governs your use of the mobile application "Knight Jump AR", for Apple iPhone, iPad, iPod, with iOS version 8.0 or later, created by John Baer.
This app uses your camera as a core function of gameplay. We do NOT store or save photos taken using the in-game camera.
Photos taken will NOT be used for any marketing, or commercial purposes. 

2. Location information
This app does NOT collect any location information for your mobile device.

3. Automatic Data Collection and Advertising
This app does not collect any statistics, aggregate or otherwise. No personal data is used.

4. California Online Privacy Protection Act Compliance
We comply with the California Online Privacy Protection Act. We therefore will not distribute your personal information to outside parties without your consent

5. Agreement
By using this mobile app, you agree to this privacy policy.

6. Contacts
If you have any questions, you can contact me through this email address: computericedtea@gmail.com. 
